law.text: Any person who violates any provision of this chapter shall be fined not less than one hundred dollars ($100) nor more than one thousand dollars ($1,000), or be imprisoned not more than three (3) months, or both.
law.history: Amended 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 214, sec. 40, effective January 1, 1999. -- Amended 1986 Ky. Acts ch. 291, sec. 38, effective July 15, 1986. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 1599e-21.
